    {
      "id": "PopularPost251285",
      "post_content": "I understand why [Pacifism](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pacifism) is rated higher than this even if others are saying its a great card. People are pointing out that this is way better than pacifism because of it's versatility. And that when you have this in your hand you have the option to ramp your mana up OR neutralize an opposing threat.   \n  \nThe problem is, using this to ramp mana up renders one of your creatures useless combat-wise because you have to tap the creature on certain turns and that is what makes this card less appealing. Now, using it as a defensive card is where the comparison to pacifism comes in. Giving the creature a mana ability becomes a drawback or sorts and that again makes this card less appealing.  \n  \nI'll still give it a 4/5 because it's a planar chaos card and that set is just crazy awesome.  \n  ",
      "posted_by": "acolyte_of_night",
      "html": "<div class=\"post oddItem\" id=\"PopularPost251285\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_post\">I understand why <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Pacifism\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Pacifism\">Pacifism</a> is rated higher than this even if others are saying its a great card. People are pointing out that this is way better than pacifism because of it's versatility. And that when you have this in your hand you have the option to ramp your mana up OR neutralize an opposing threat. <br/><br/>The problem is, using this to ramp mana up renders one of your creatures useless combat-wise because you have to tap the creature on certain turns and that is what makes this card less appealing. Now, using it as a defensive card is where the comparison to pacifism comes in. Giving the creature a mana ability becomes a drawback or sorts and that again makes this card less appealing.<br/><br/>I'll still give it a 4/5 because it's a planar chaos card and that set is just crazy awesome.<br/><br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl09_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '251285'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy82534\">acolyte_of_night</span>\r\n                                (6/15/2012 1:05:18 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"po